<section class="py-20 px-6 md:px-16 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 md:gap-16">
    <!-- Left Column: Heading + Image -->
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
      <!-- Top Heading -->
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-gray-900">About Us</h1>

      <!-- Image Below Heading -->
      <img
        src="/Images/aboutus.jpg"
        alt="About Us"
        class="w-full h-auto max-h-[550px] object-cover rounded-xl shadow-md"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Right Column: Content aligned to top -->
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center text-gray-600 text-lg space-y-5">
      <!-- Right Heading -->
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
         YOUR TRUSTED VASTU CONSULTANTS
      </h2>

      <p class="text-[15px]">
        Founded by childhood friends V.K. Lokesh and Aran V, our Vastu
        consultancy blends architectural expertise with traditional and
        astrological wisdom.
      </p>

      <p class="text-[15px]">
        V.K. Lokesh is a registered architect with a postgraduation in
        Environmental Architecture from McGAN’s Ooty (2024) and trained as a
        Stapathi at the Govt. College of Architecture and Sculpture. His
        portfolio includes heritage conservation projects with the World
        Monument Fund, IIT-M, and TNHRNC.
      </p>

      <p class="text-[15px]">
        Aran is an engineer from CEG (2015) and IIM-Trichy alumnus with deep
        expertise in Vastu, astrology, violet flame healing, and angel healing.
        Trained under experts like Abhishek Goel, Pankit Goel, and Saavi Jain,
        they’ve researched Vastu Shastra and Temple Science since 2019. With 50+
        successful projects, we offer personalized, result-driven Vastu
        solutions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
